revision.text:
An '''acid house party''' was a type of illegal [[party]] typically staged in warehouses in 1987–89. In the [[United Kingdom]], the most famous illegal party promoters were [[Genesis'88]], [[Sunrise / Back to the Future|Sunrise]], and Energy. Eventually the acid house parties morphed into the modern [[rave]] scene.<ref>''Class of 88 - The True Acid House Experience'', Wayne Anthony, Virgin. The book may also be downloaded from the [https://groups.yahoo.com/group/acidhouse88/ - author's e-group]. </ref>
